column5: What area? I could probably arrange one for you if you'd like. Depending on the day and area.

Well... I'm out of Morson, so that's a bit of a haul. I'm sure you'll be able to find someone over there though. Wish I could be of more help.
Try Rob Horley, he guides out of Sioux Narrows and is a very successful bass tournament fisherman also (807) 226-5742.
